<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content="text/html; charset=UTF-8" http-equiv="Content-Type" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h2 style="color: red">FOR FITSBY EMPLOYEES ONLY</h2><br/>
    <h3>This user just worked out at an unverified gym and requested that we verify it:</h3>
    <p>
      <strong>Description</strong>: <%= @string %><br/>
      <strong>User ID</strong>: <%= @user.id %><br/>
      <strong>User Email</strong>: <%= @user_email %><br/>
      <strong>Gym Name (downcased)</strong>: <%= @gym_name %><br/>
      <strong>Geo Latitude</strong>: <%= @geo_lat %><br/>
      <strong>Geo Longitude</strong>: <%= @geo_long %><br/>
      <strong>Number of requests this user has made for this gym</strong>: <%= @number_of_requests %><br/>
    </p><br/>
    
    <span>Go into PGAdmin and change the column called "decision" in the table called "decidedlocations" (where 1 means "blacklisted" and is not a real gym, and 0 means "whitelisted" and means that the gym is good to go.</span>
  </body>
</html>